ced by employing interview techniques that maximize deceivers' cognitive load, while allowing truth‐tellers the opportunity to respond to evidence incrementally. ", 'original': None}', 'Authors': "[{'first_name': 'Coral J.', 'last_name': 'Dando', 'initials': None, 'researcher_id': 'ur.07447737153.42', 'grid_ids': array(['grid.6374.6'], dtype=object), 'orcid': array(['0000-0002-6196-8475'], dtype=object), 'corresponding': True, 'raw_affiliations': array(['Department of Psychology, University of Wolverhampton, UK'],
