 and the coupling agents.', 'original': None}", 'Authors': "[{'first_name': 'Yonghui', 'last_name': 'Zhou', 'initials': None, 'researcher_id': 'ur.0671006300.83', 'grid_ids': array(['grid.256111.0', 'grid.7728.a'], dtype=object), 'orcid': array([], dtype=object), 'corresponding': False, 'raw_affiliations': array(['College of Materials Engineering, Fujian Agriculture and Forestry University, PR China',
