dents of trust in e-government adoption.", 'original': None}', 'Authors': "[{'first_name': 'Latifa', 'last_name': 'Alzahrani', 'initials': None, 'researcher_id': 'ur.013614603233.24', 'grid_ids': array(['grid.7728.a'], dtype=object), 'orcid': array(['0000-0003-3182-0813'], dtype=object), 'corresponding': True, 'raw_affiliations': array(['College of Business, Arts and Social Sciences, Brunel Business School, Brunel University London, Uxbridge, UB8 3PH, United Kingdom'],
