 the take-up of energy retrofits.', 'original': None}", 'Authors': "[{'first_name': 'Rajat', 'last_name': 'Gupta', 'initials': None, 'researcher_id': 'ur.014642245325.02', 'grid_ids': array(['grid.7628.b'], dtype=object), 'orcid': array(['0000-0001-8959-0251'], dtype=object), 'corresponding': True, 'raw_affiliations': array(['Low Carbon Building Research Group, Oxford Institute for Sustainable Development, School of Architecture, Oxford Brookes University, Oxford, UK'],
