mmendations for the use of such events in event tourism settings.', 'original': None}", 'Authors': "[{'first_name': 'Maren', 'last_name': 'Viol', 'initials': None, 'researcher_id': 'ur.07770457267.34', 'grid_ids': array(['grid.20409.3f'], dtype=object), 'orcid': array(['0000-0002-5668-6721'], dtype=object), 'corresponding': True, 'raw_affiliations': array(['The Business School, Edinburgh Napier University, Craiglockhart Campus, 219 Colinton Road, Edinburgh, EH14 1DJ, UK'],
