 cost arguments when trying to encourage small businesses towards greater environmental engagement. These findings suggest that public policy and business advice in this area should perhaps focus more strongly on personal values and a sense of being able to contribute to environmental protection in their engagement with small businesses. Copyright © 2012 John Wiley & Sons, Ltd and ERP Environment.', 'original': None}", 'Authors': "[{'first_name': 'Sarah', 'last_name': 'Williams', 'initials': None, 'researcher_id': None, 'grid_ids': array(['grid.10837.3d'], dtype=object), 'orcid': array([], dtype=object), 'corresponding': False, 'raw_affiliations': array(['Open University, UK'], dtype=object), 'affiliations_address': array([{'grid_id': 'grid.10837.3d', 'city_id': 2642465, 'state_code': None, 'country_code': 'GB', 'raw_affiliation': 'Open University, UK'}],
